      • isDependent

        boolean isDependent(Decision d1,
                    Decision d0,
                    java.lang.String option,
                    java.util.List<Solution> allSolutions)
        Parameters:
        d1 - decision d1
        d0 - decision d0
        option - selected option
        allSolutions - all generated solutions.
        Returns:
        true if decision d1 is dependent on selection of option 'option' in decision d0; in other words, if d1 is null every time 'option' is not selected in d0. Formally: isDependent(d1, d0, option) iff for all s: solution| s.selection(d0) != option imples s.selection(d1) == null
